message: Hi Bob, I'm offering you my product for $11,000. It's in excellent condition and worth every penny. Let me know what you think!
Hi Alice, thank you for the offer. I understand the value of your product, but I am only able to pay up to $9,500 for it. I hope this proposal works for you!
Bob, I appreciate your offer, but $9,500 is a bit too low for me. I'm willing to come down to $10,500.  This is a fair price considering the product's value. Let's see if we can reach an agreement.
